subject: Call For Papers
from: "The Society of Digital Information and Wireless Communications (SDIWC)" <donotreply@sdiwc.us>
body:
The World Congress on Computing and Information Technology (WCIT) ( http://sdiwc.net/conferences/2013/wcit/) have the following conferences.

Please consider submitting a paper or more to one conference or all if possible.

+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
Name: The Second International Conference on Digital Enterprise and Information Systems (DEIS 2013)
URL: http://sdiwc.net/conferences/2013/Malaysia1/
Dates: March 4-6, 2013
Contact: de@sdiwc.net
+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
Name: The Second International Conference on e-Technologies and Networks for Development (ICeNd 2013)
URL: http://sdiwc.net/conferences/2013/Malaysia2/
Dates: March 4-6, 2013
Contact: ice@sdiwc.net
+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
Name: The Second International Conference on Cyber Security, Cyber Warfare and Digital Forensic (CyberSec 2013)
URL: http://sdiwc.net/conferences/2013/Malaysia3
Dates: March 4-6, 2013
Contact: cyb@sdiwc.net
+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
Name: The First International Conference on Green Computing, Technology and Innovation (ICGCTI 2013)
URL: http://sdiwc.net/conferences/2013/Malaysia4/
Dates: March 4-6, 2013
Contact: icg@sdiwc.net
+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+

Please note that you can submit keynote and tutorial proposals, as well as other types of session proposals.

Please forward this message to as many potentially interested people as possible. Thank You in advance.

Inquiries can be forwarded to:
+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+
Natalie Walker
The Society of Digital Information and Wireless Communications (SDIWC)
Kowloon, Hongkong
www.sdiwc.net
